<h2>Security Alert 🔒</h2>

<p>Hi {{name}},</p>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p><strong>⚠️ Unusual Activity Detected</strong></p>
  <p>We detected {{alertType}} on your account.</p>
</div>

<h3>Details:</h3>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>📅 Date:</strong> {{formatDate timestamp}}</p>
  <p><strong>🌍 Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
  <p><strong>🌐 IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</p>
  <p><strong>🖥️ Device:</strong> {{device}}</p>
  <p><strong>🔍 Activity:</strong> {{activity}}</p>
</div>

<h3>Was this you?</h3>

<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin: 20px 0;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding-right: 10px;">
      <a href="{{confirmUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">Yes, This Was Me</a>
    </td>
    <td>
      <a href="{{secureUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary" style="background-color: #dc3545; color: #ffffff;">No, Secure My Account</a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p><strong>If this wasn't you:</strong></p>
  <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
    <li>Click "Secure My Account" immediately</li>
    <li>Change your password</li>
    <li>Review your recent activity</li>
    <li>Contact support if needed</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p>We take security seriously. If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Coffee App Security Team</p>
